title: How Much Can You Stafford?
description:
Mina talks to Sheil Kapadia of The Athletic about what should be a wild offseason with an ample amount of QB needy teams, how Aaron Rodgers was let down by both his teammates and coaches in the NFC Championship Game, and what the Bills need to do to improve heading into next year.
